{"tid":2287922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：之鋒突破盲腸 譚惠珠「踢爆」港官扮愛國（李八方）","createTime":"2020-11-16T06:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T06:32:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a90dbdad4dbe5c27ca0abde7acf969ca32d862","tid":2287922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201116/3JKX7ZR7PBFDVHFXCUE6LF4DM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201116%2F3JKX7ZR7PBFDVHFXCUE6LF4DM4%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3vkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=d455709d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201116%2F3JKX7ZR7PBFDVHFXCUE6LF4DM4%2F&h=ea9e74af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201116/3JKX7ZR7PBFDVHFXCUE6LF4DM4/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：之鋒突破盲腸 譚惠珠「踢爆」港官扮愛國（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hw9KZZwBojXVAKo1QTxvDBByUDk=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6LGSMGZF3BEOHJ7DDV5CCQ3ZFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fhw9KZZwBojXVAKo1QTxvDBByUDk%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6LGSMGZF3BEOHJ7DDV5CCQ3ZFM.jpg&h=b1aed875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚惠珠<br />\n<br />\n話說基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠出席電視節目被問到DQ立會議員有冇違反程序公義，佢即刻話「12名官員」（應為11個）被美國制裁，「對呢12個官員都係冇程序公義，事前完全冇警告，如果佢哋有家人喺美國，咁咪都唔可以去探佢哋屋企人！」<br />\n<br />\n聽譚惠珠咁講，又似乎有佢嘅道理喎！不過，成日提醒愛國愛港人士唔好只得把口愛國嘅之鋒，今次又突破盲腸！佢喺其fb專頁轉貼譚惠珠有關言論嘅報道，之後加多句反問譚 ：「咁愛中國，點解屋企人要喺美國？」之鋒咁問又啱喎，今天中國有錢又有機會，又有經濟雙循環又有大灣區，作為愛國愛港人士，點解仲會有屋企人喺美國？唔叫佢哋返祖國共享繁榮呢？<br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}